t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    (x1, y1) = map(int, input().split(' '))
    (xb, yb) = map(int, input().split(' '))
    (x3, y3) = map(int, input().split(' '))
    xa = min(x1, x3)
    ya = min(y1, y3)
    xc = max(x1, x3)
    yc = max(y1, y3)
    if xb == xa and ya <= yb <= yc or (yb == yc and xa <= xb <= xc):
        print('YES')
    elif yb == ya and xa <= xb <= xc or (xb == xc and ya <= yb <= yc):
        print('YES')
    else:
        print('NO')

t = int(input())
while t:
    (ax, ay) = map(int, input().split())
    (bx, by) = map(int, input().split())
    (cx, cy) = map(int, input().split())
    condition1 = ax == bx and cy == by
    condition2 = ay == by and cx == bx
    condition3 = ax == bx and cx == bx and (bx > ax and bx < cx or (bx < ax and bx > cx))
    condition4 = ay == by and cy == by and (by > ay and by < cy or (by < ay and by > cy))
    condition5 = (ax == bx or cx == bx) and (by > ay and by < cy or (by < ay and by > cy))
    condition6 = (ay == by or cy == by) and (bx > ax and bx < cx or (bx < ax and bx > cx))
    if condition1 or condition2 or condition3 or condition4 or condition5 or condition6:
        print('YES')
    else:
        print('NO')
    t -= 1

    xmi = min(xa, xc)
    ymi = min(ya, yc)
    yma = max(ya, yc)

        c += 1

t = int(input())
for i in range(0, t):

    bottom = min(Ya, Yc)

            ans = 'True'
    if bottom <= Yb and Yb <= top:
        if Xb == left or Xb == right:
            ans = 'True'
    print('YES' if ans else 'NO')
